summary: An ordinance providing for the rezoning of that unplatted tract of land lying between the north and south lines of Lot 5, Block 15, Lake Union Shore Lands extended southwesterly, and the vacated alley adjoining located on the easterly side of Fuhrman Avenue at the east end of Gwinn Place, with respect to use and Area Districts, and amending Ordinance No. 45382, as amended, by adding thereto two new sections numbered 2-12 and 17-11 respectively.
